# ── Build outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anchored to the repo root with a leading slash so it does NOT also match the
# test fixture's directory (test/fixtures/source-root/usr/bin/), which IS tracked.
/bin/

# ── Docker ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sentinel file written by `make build/test/…` to track dev-image freshness.
# Local only — not committed.
/.docker-build

# ── Release artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated by git-cliff at the repo root during the release workflow.
/RELEASE_NOTES.md

# ── Runtime outputs (apt2distroless itself) ────────────────────────────────
# The tool writes these at runtime; they should not be accidentally committed
# if someone runs apt2distroless with the repo as the target. Left unanchored on
# purpose — these can be written next to any target directory.
*.manifest.jsonl
/tmp/

# ── Go toolchain & test artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vendor directory (not used; modules are managed via go.mod/go.sum).
vendor/
# Compiled test binaries (`go test -c`) and coverage/profile output.
*.test
coverage.out
coverage.html
*.prof

# ── Editor & OS noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
